    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as they did when new. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car that has been meticulously cared for and kept in a climate-controlled environment.",
