    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, but a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational, making this a dependable and comfortable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 33000.0,
